A GOODNIGHT BOOKSTORE PRIVATE BLOG POST

738
01:00:12,442 --> 01:00:13,735
POSTED BY SEOP

739
01:00:14,235 --> 01:00:16,696
I was the son of a vagrant
who lived in the mountains,

740
01:00:16,779 --> 01:00:18,364
and one day, I was abandoned.

741
01:00:19,157 --> 01:00:23,578
My adoptive parents raised me.

742
01:00:24,245 --> 01:00:28,333
Though I did not view it as a weakness,

743
01:00:29,000 --> 01:00:33,212
there were some people
who wished that this would hurt me.

744
01:00:34,047 --> 01:00:35,673
"Aren't you unhappy?"

745
01:00:35,757 --> 01:00:38,593
"Didn't you use to live in a cabin
in the back mountains?"

746
01:00:39,385 --> 01:00:43,431
"Wasn't your father a vagrant?"

747
01:00:44,223 --> 01:00:48,311
Should I be as unhappy and sad
as they wished I were?

748
01:00:49,228 --> 01:00:53,399
I thought long and hard about it, but no.

749
01:00:54,067 --> 01:00:56,319
I concluded that I have
no reason to be unhappy

750
01:00:56,402 --> 01:00:58,529
when I have people
I'm grateful for in my life.

751
01:00:59,155 --> 01:01:05,411
Anyway, it's all in the past now.

752
01:01:09,916 --> 01:01:12,627
I'm sleepy.
But I want to keep looking at you.

753
01:01:12,710 --> 01:01:13,586
Is this Eun-sil?

754
01:01:13,670 --> 01:01:16,673
Actually, I have something I want to ask.
Is that okay?

755
01:01:16,756 --> 01:01:20,301
This is a new member of the book club.
Round of applause!

756
01:01:20,385 --> 01:01:21,844
What is this? Explain.

757
01:01:21,928 --> 01:01:24,180
I'm talking about
the fax you sent yesterday.

758
01:01:24,263 --> 01:01:25,973
Did you come to return that?

759
01:01:26,057 --> 01:01:27,141
This was an excuse.

760
01:01:27,225 --> 01:01:28,643
The truth is, I liked you.

761
01:01:28,726 --> 01:01:31,729
I liked you first for a very long time.

762
01:01:31,813 --> 01:01:33,106
What am I going to do?

763
01:01:33,189 --> 01:01:36,776
I don't think I'll ever forget
the way you look right now.

